OL,3,CFujitsu received #3.4bn from Treasury-
OL,4,Clinked contracts since 2019, MPs find
OL,6,FFujitsu received more than #3.4
OL,7,Fbillion through contracts running with
OL,8,FTreasury-linked organisations since
OL,9,F2019 despite its role in the Post
OL,10,FOffice scandal, MPs have found.
OL,12,FAround #1.4 billion worth of deals
OL,13,Fhave been awarded since the High Court
OL,14,Fruled that there had been numerous
OL,15,Fbugs and errors in its Horizon
OL,16,Fsoftware.
OL,18,FMore than #2 billion worth of deals
OL,19,Fwere agreed before 2019 and remained
OL,20,Factive in the following period, the
OL,21,FCommons Treasury Committee said.
