OL,3,CFujitsu received #3.4bn from Treasury-
OL,4,Clinked contracts since 2019, MPs find
OL,6,FThe influential group of MPs last
OL,7,Fmonth wrote to organisations including
OL,8,FHM Revenue and Customs (HMRC), the
OL,9,FFinancial Conduct Authority (FCA) and
OL,10,Fthe Bank of England (BoE) to demand
OL,11,Fdetails of their agreements with
OL,12,FFujitsu.
OL,14,FPublishing the responses on Saturday,
OL,15,Fthe committee revealed that all three
OL,16,Fhave spent considerable sums with
OL,17,FFujitsu Services Ltd or Fujitsu Global-
OL,18,Fowned entities.
