OL,6,FHMRC has awarded the company eight
OL,7,Fcontracts worth #1.39 billion since
OL,8,Fthe ruling in 2019, while a further
OL,9,Fsix contracts pre-dating the ruling
OL,10,Fremained active after 2019 but have
OL,11,Fsince ceased.
OL,13,FThe FCA agreed deals worth around #630
OL,14,Fmillion dating back to 2007 which
OL,15,Fcontinued to run after the High Court
OL,16,Fjudgment, and still maintains six
OL,17,Fcontracts worth a combined total of
OL,18,Faround #9 million.
