OL,3,CFujitsu received #3.4bn from Treasury-
OL,4,Clinked contracts since 2019, MPs find
OL,6,FHundreds of subpostmasters across the
OL,7,FUK were wrongly prosecuted between
OL,8,F2015 and 2019 after Fujitsu's faulty
OL,9,Faccounting system made it seem as
OL,10,Fthough money was missing from their
OL,11,Fbranches.
OL,13,FIn 2019, the High Court ruled the
OL,14,Fsoftware had contained "bugs, errors
OL,15,Fand defects", leading the scandal to
OL,16,Fbecome known as the most widespread
OL,17,Fmiscarriage of justice in British
OL,18,Fhistory.
